Definition: a new religion founded by L. Ron Hubbard in 1955 and characterized by a belief in the power of a person's spirit to clear itself of past painful experiences through self-knowledge and spiritual fulfillment
Synonyms: Church_of_Scientology, religion, a, new, founded, by, L, Ron, Hubbard, in, and, characterized, belief, the, power, of, person, s, spirit, to, clear, itself, past, painful, experiences, through, self-knowledge, spiritual, fulfillment
Category: noun.group
